CloudFunctions --> FeeManagement
CloudFunctions --> PaymentManagement
CloudFunctions --> ResourceManagement
CloudFunctions --> AnnouncementManagement
CloudFunctions --> NotificationManagement
CloudFunctions --> Reporting
CloudFunctions --> Audit

note right of Authorization
  Security Boundary:
  - Role validation
  - Institute isolation
  - Ownership checks
  - Least privilege
end note

note bottom of Audit
  All privileged lifecycle changes
  publish immutable audit records.
end note
@enduml
